## Findings
- Profile section: The director's photo and message block are displayed correctly. In mobile view, they stack vertically (photo -> name -> message) and look professional.
- Access section: The info table and Google Maps are side-by-side in desktop view and stack vertically in mobile view. The layout is clean and responsive.
- Quality: No horizontal overflow or layout breakage was observed. The design reflects a professional Japanese corporate site appropriate for a judicial scrivener office.
